hema.json:26:        \"description\": \"Description of the strategy workflow and behavior.\"\n../3312-20a114be/forge/schemas/strategy_schema.json:36:        \"description\": \"Workflow strategy implementation name.\"\n../3312-20a114be/forge/schemas/strategy_schema.json:46:        \"description\": \"Model identifier to run for this strategy.\"\n../3312-20a114be/forge/schemas/strategy_schema.json:71:        \"description\": \"Optional tunable parameters for the strategy.\",\n../3312-20a114be/forge/schemas/strategy_schema.json:96:        \"description\": \"List of MCP configuration identifiers to enable for this strategy.\",\n../3312-20a114be/forge/schemas/strategy_schema.json:113:          \"initial\": \"prompts/strategy/baseline/initial.md\",\n../3312-20a114be/forge/schemas/strategy_schema.json:114:          \"after-successful-iteration\": \"prompts/strategy/baseline/after_success.md\",\n../3312-20a114be/forge/schemas/strategy_schema.json:115:          \"after-failed-iteration\": \"prompts/strategy/baseline/after_fail.md\"\n../3312-20a114be/forge/docs/functional-spec.md:21:2. **Coverage improvement** — increase dynamic-access coverage of\n../3312-20a114be/forge/docs/functional-spec.md:33:   dynamic-access coverage of already-supported libraries.\n../3312-20a114be/forge/docs/functional-spec.md:49:| **Workflow strategy** | A registered control loop in [ai_workflows/workflow_strategies/](../ai_workflows/workflow_strategies/) (e.g. `basic_iterative`, `dynamic_access_iterative`). |\n../3312-20a114be/forge/docs/functional-spec.md:50:| **Predefined strategy** | Named, fully parameterized combination of agent + workflow strategy + prompts + parameters in [strategies/predefined_strategies.json](../strategies/predefined_strategies.json). Selected via `--strategy-name`. |\n../3312-20a114be/forge/docs/functional-spec.md:51:| **Post-generation intervention** | Recovery step a strategy invokes when the post-iteration `./gradlew test` still fails. Pluggable via the `PostGenerationI